---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<MainLayout title="Email Security | Coro Cybersecurity — Blue Cap IT" description="Coro email security blocks phishing, business email compromise, malware, and spam before they reach your inbox. Works with Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <img src="/images/coro-email-hero.jpg" alt="Blue 3D mail icon representing secure email communication" style="width:100%;height:auto;max-height:340px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);" />
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="cybersecurity.html">Cybersecurity</a> <span>/</span> Email Security</div>
      <div class="section-label">Coro Cybersecurity</div>
      <h1>Email <span class="grad">Security</span></h1>
      <p class="section-sub">Email is the #1 attack vector for businesses. Coro blocks phishing, business email compromise, malware attachments, and spam before they ever reach your inbox.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Why Coro Email Security</div>
          <h2>Stop Threats Before <span class="grad">They Land</span></h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Over 90% of cyberattacks start with a phishing email. Coro's AI-powered email security scans every inbound and outbound message for malicious content, suspicious links, impersonation attempts, and data leaks — stopping attacks before your team ever sees them.</p>
          <p class="section-sub" style="margin-top:1rem;">Works seamlessly with Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace. Blue Cap IT handles the full setup and ongoing management.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
            <a href="cybersecurity.html" class="btn-ghost">View All Coro Modules</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul class="why-list">
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:fish" /></div>
            <div><h4>Anti-Phishing</h4><p>AI analyzes email content, sender reputation, and link destinations to catch phishing attempts — even sophisticated spear-phishing targeted at specific employees.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:user" /></div>
            <div><h4>Impersonation Protection</h4><p>Detects business email compromise (BEC) where attackers impersonate executives, vendors, or trusted contacts to trick employees into transferring funds or sharing data.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:paperclip" /></div>
            <div><h4>Malware &amp; Attachment Scanning</h4><p>Every attachment is scanned and sandboxed before delivery. Malicious files are quarantined automatically — even zero-day threats.</p></div>
          </li>
          <li class="why-item">
            <div class="why-icon"><Icon name="lucide:link" /></div>
            <div><h4>URL Protection</h4><p>Links in emails are checked in real time at the moment of click. If a link becomes malicious after delivery, Coro still blocks it.</p></div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background:var(--surface);">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div style="text-align:center;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 2rem;">
        <div class="section-label">Key Capabilities</div>
        <h2>What Coro Email <span class="grad">Security Covers</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="products-grid">
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:fish" /></div>
          <h3>Phishing Prevention</h3>
          <p>AI-powered analysis of email content, headers, and sender behavior catches phishing attempts that basic spam filters miss.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:briefcase" /></div>
          <h3>Business Email Compromise</h3>
          <p>Detects impersonation of executives and trusted contacts. Flags suspicious requests for wire transfers, gift cards, or credential sharing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:bug" /></div>
          <h3>Malware Protection</h3>
          <p>Attachments are detonated in a secure sandbox. Malicious payloads are blocked before they reach any endpoint.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:upload" /></div>
          <h3>Outbound DLP</h3>
          <p>Monitors outgoing emails for sensitive data — credit card numbers, social security numbers, health records — and prevents accidental or malicious data leaks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:search" /></div>
          <h3>Quarantine &amp; Review</h3>
          <p>Suspicious emails are quarantined for admin review. Users can request release of false positives directly from the quarantine digest.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product-card">
          <div class="pcard-icon"><Icon name="lucide:cloud" /></div>
          <h3>M365 &amp; Google Integration</h3>
          <p>Connects directly to Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace via API — no MX record changes, no mail flow disruptions, no downtime during setup.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Secure Your Inbox</div>
    <h2>Get Coro Email Security<br/><span class="grad">from Blue Cap IT</span></h2>
    <p>Contact us for a free email security assessment. We'll show you the threats your current setup is missing — and how Coro can stop them.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost"><Icon name="lucide:phone" /> (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost"><Icon name="lucide:mail" /> info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
